  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bcb\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc7 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A scuffle between people queuing for petrol in Atton",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "A scuffle broke out between people queuing to get fuel at the Aton IOC petrol filling station. Due to this, a tense situation has arisen there.",
        "This tension arose because some people tried to push their close friends into the middle of the queue and some people tried to get petrol without joining the queue.",
        "A week later to the IOC filling station in Attan. The petrol bowser arrived at two o'clock in the morning on Monday 04th. The fuel unloaded from it is being distributed.",
        "It is worth noting that many people who have been waiting for the last two or three days to fill up petrol have come to get fuel today."
      ],
